mailfilter: The Anti-Spam Utility
mailfilter: 
mailfilter: Mailfilter is a flexible utility for UNIX (-like) operating
mailfilter: systems to get rid of unwanted spam mails, before having to go
mailfilter: through the trouble of downloading them into the local computer.
mailfilter: It offers support for one or many POP3 accounts and is especially
mailfilter: useful for dialup connections via modem, ISDN, etc.
mailfilter: Install Mailfilter if you'd like to remove spam from your POP mail accounts
